sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Datum Platform
    participant API as FastAPI Server
    participant Orch as Orchestrator
    participant PG as PostGIS
    participant Drone as Drone Fleet
    participant LLM as LiteLLM (GPT-5.4)
    participant OAI as OpenAI Embeddings

    Client->>API: POST /orchestrate
    API->>Orch: orchestrate(req)

    Note over Orch,PG: 1. Create run record
    Orch->>PG: INSERT orchestration_runs

    Note over Orch,PG: 2. Spatial context
    Orch->>PG: ST_DWithin nearby facts
    PG-->>Orch: facts + contradictions + gaps

    Note over Orch: 3. Select skills
    Orch->>Orch: keyword match SKILL.md

    Note over Orch,Drone: 4. Dispatch
    Orch->>Drone: POST /task (enriched)
    Drone-->>Orch: {taskId, status: queued}

    Note over Orch,Drone: 5. Poll
    loop Every 5s until complete
        Orch->>Drone: GET /task/{id}
        Drone-->>Orch: {status, output}
    end

    Note over Orch,OAI: 6. Ingest
    Orch->>LLM: Extract findings (JSON)
    LLM-->>Orch: [{content, lat, lon, ...}]

    loop Each finding
        Orch->>OAI: Embed text
        OAI-->>Orch: vector[1536]
        Orch->>PG: INSERT knowledge_facts
        Orch->>LLM: Detect contradictions
        LLM-->>Orch: {contradicted: [...]}
        opt Contradictions found
            Orch->>PG: UPDATE invalid_at
        end
    end

    Note over Orch,PG: 7. Score + Drift
    Orch->>PG: UPDATE outcome_quality
    Orch->>PG: Drift sweep (3 checks)

    Orch-->>API: RunStatus
    API-->>Client: {id, facts_extracted, quality}
